title: Chamberlin's Natural Foods Market - Lakeland
description: Natural foods and supplements store with several locations in the Orlando area. This location has a small organic produce section, a few aisles of organic grocery items, variety of vegan milks and vegan cheeses, several meat-alternative products, international foods such as falafel mixes and nori sheets, a large collection of supplements including vegan protein sources, earth-friendly toiletries and cleaning products, and a gluten-free section. The staff is knowledgeable, and you can take free educational material about nutrition home with you.
